The [[!template id=freenode_irc bitcoin]] channel on freenode serves as the de-facto "front door" for newcomers on IRC. Therefore, we strive to maintain a professional,  friendly, and helpful atmosphere on the channel at all times. To this  effect, the following behaviors are expressly prohibited: 

* Insults, flamewars, trolling;
* Discussion of unlawful activity, pursuant to [freenode's guidelines](http://freenode.net/policy.shtml#unlawful);
* Generally, anything that would make a newcomer feel unwelcome or would reflect badly on the bitcoin community is to be avoided.
Private chat and alternative channels are always available, make good use of them.
